OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784908087
OL,3,CHuge fire spreads across 200 acres of
OL,4,Cheathland on Isle of Wight
OL,6,FDozens of firefighters are tackling a
OL,7,Fgorse fire on the Isle of Wight which
OL,8,Fhas spread over nearly 200 acres of
OL,9,Fheathland in Headon Warren since it
OL,10,Fbroke out this morning (Thursday July
OL,11,F23).
OL,13,FTeams have been working all day to
OL,14,Fcontain the fire which was first
OL,15,Freported at 9:12am. It initially
OL,16,Fspread over an area approximately 200
OL,17,Fmetres by 250 metres.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
