FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784908087
OL,3,CHuge fire spreads across 200 acres of
OL,4,Cheathland on Isle of Wight
OL,6,FBy 1pm, however, it had grown rapidly
OL,7,Fcovering an area 800 metres by 400
OL,8,Fmetres prompting crews from across
OL,9,FHampshire to respond with 14 fire
OL,10,Fengines on the scene by mid afternoon.
OL,12,FWightLink Ferries says it helped
OL,13,Ftransport nine fire engines to the
OL,14,Fisland while farmers in the local area
OL,15,Fare understood to have used their
OL,16,Ftractors as fire breaks to help crews.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
