OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784908087
OL,3,CHuge fire spreads across 200 acres of
OL,4,Cheathland on Isle of Wight
OL,6,FIn its latest update at 6pm, Hampshire
OL,7,Fand Isle of Wight Fire and Rescue
OL,8,FService said 80 firefighters were at
OL,9,Fthe scene - now covering 1000 metres
OL,10,Fby 800 metres - and would be working
OL,11,Fthrough the night to contain the
OL,12,Fheathland fire.
OL,14,FIn a statement on its website, the
OL,15,Ffire service said. "We have around 80
OL,16,Ffirefighters now working to extinguish
OL,17,Fthe large heathland fire at Headon
OL,18,FWarren on the Isle of Wight.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784908087
OL,3,CHuge fire spreads across 200 acres of
OL,4,Cheathland on Isle of Wight
OL,6,F"The crews who were first in
OL,7,Fattendance this morning, and have
OL,8,Fworked incredibly hard throughout the
OL,9,Fday, are set to hand over to fresh
OL,10,Fteams arriving on the scene this
OL,11,Fevening."
OL,13,FThey added: "Our teams continue to
OL,14,Fwork hard in difficult conditions,
OL,15,Ftackling a 1,000m x 800m fire on
OL,16,Fchallenging terrain.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
