PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1784908087
OL,3,CHuge fire spreads across 200 acres of
OL,4,Cheathland on Isle of Wight
OL,6,F"We have firefighters from Newport,
OL,7,FCowes, Ventnor, Freshwater, Shanklin,
OL,8,FEast Cowes, Ryde and Sandown in
OL,9,Fattendance, and they are supported by
OL,10,Fmainland teams from Southsea,
OL,11,FLymington, Emsworth, Portchester, St
OL,12,FMary's, Hardley, Havant and Hightown."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/5
